      <title><![CDATA[What would you do?]]></title>
      <introduction_text><![CDATA[<p>You are deep frying chips and the phone rings. You rush to answer it and when you return, the saucepan of oil is on fire. </p>
<p>What is the best thing to do? Select one of the two <strong>Decision Point Hot Spots</strong>. </p>]]></introduction_text>
