    <item>
      <id>DP2</id>
      <type>mp_decision_point</type>
      <title><![CDATA[Correct choice]]></title>
      <introduction_text><![CDATA[<p>That's the right choice. If it is safe for you to turn off the gas or power do that first. As the fire may be uncontrollable and move around as it is blown by the breeze it would be wise to cover your arm  in a thick damp towel as you reach forward to turn the gas off. </p>
<p>Now make your next choice. There is still some flame in the frypan - what should you do now?</p>
<p> </p>]]></introduction_text>
